 972    /// <summary>
 973    /// Applies skip/take pagination window to an async enumerable of feature records.
 974    /// </summary>
 975    private static IAsyncEnumerable<FeatureRecord> ApplyPaginationWindow(
 976        IAsyncEnumerable<FeatureRecord> source,
 977        int skip,
 978        int? take)
 0979    {
 0980        var enforceSkip = skip > 0;
 0981        var enforceTake = take.HasValue && take.Value >= 0;
 0982        if (!enforceSkip && !enforceTake)
 0983        {
 0984            return source;
 985        }
 986
 0987        return Window();
 988
 989        async IAsyncEnumerable<FeatureRecord> Window()
 0990        {
 0991            var remainingSkip = enforceSkip ? Math.Max(0, skip) : 0;
 0992            var remainingTake = enforceTake ? take!.Value : int.MaxValue;
 993
 0994            await foreach (var record in source)
 0995            {
 0996                if (enforceSkip && remainingSkip > 0)
 0997                {
 0998                    remainingSkip--;
 0999                    continue;
 1000                }
 01001                if (enforceTake && remainingTake <= 0)
 01002                {
 01003                    yield break;
 1004                }
 01005                if (enforceTake) remainingTake--;
 1006
 01007                yield return record;
 01008            }
 01009        }
 01010    }
